###
# @name get-id
GET http://0.0.0.0:3000/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{$global.jwtToken}}


# @name make-admin
PATCH http://0.0.0.0:3000/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{$global.jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "userType" : 1
}


