}


###
# @name update-user
PATCH http://0.0.0.0:3000/users/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{$global.jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "username" : "uwuw",
    "email" : "uwuw@workout.com",
    "userType" : 1
}

###
# @name delete-user

DELETE http://0.0.0.0:3000/user/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{$global.jwtToken}}


### 
